    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "@Adamski: Because it&#39;s not <code>&lt;X,Y&gt;</code>, it&#39;s <code>&lt;Key,Value&gt;</code>. He&#39;s not asking for an arbitrary <code>Pair</code> type, he&#39;s asking for a <code>KeyValuePair</code> type."
