      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "This isn&#39;t a universally-available language feature and will require more than a standard JRE runtime. <code>Pair</code> comes from javafx.util, which introduces a dependency on JavaFX, such as OracleJDK, OpenJDK or OpenJFX. If you&#39;re using one of these Java runtimes then great, but  there&#39;s no trivial way to add this to a JRE installation with a Maven or Gradle dependency."
