    "body" : "<p>The Pair class from Commons Lang might help:</p>\n\n<pre><code>Pair&lt;String, String&gt; keyValue = new ImmutablePair(\"key\", \"value\");\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Of course, you would need to include commons-lang.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 321080,
      "reputation" : 3494,
      "user_id" : 639691,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 49,
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/gwKaK.png?s=256",
      "display_name" : "Neoheurist",
