    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Use of <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javafx/2/api/javafx/util/Pair.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">javafx.util.Pair</a> is sufficient for most simple Key-Value pairings of any two types that can be instantiated.</p>\n\n<pre><code>Pair&lt;Integer, String&gt; myPair = new Pair&lt;&gt;(7, \"Seven\");\nInteger key = myPair.getKey();\nString value = myPair.getValue();\n</code></pre>\n"
