      "body" : "You seem to have missed part of his qualifications in this question.  A collection does not fit the need of a single key value pair.  He mentions the type of single Map entry, <code>Map.Entry&lt;K,V&gt;</code> but wanted a more general case.  This type can be instantiated directly though, see this answer: <a href=\"http://stackoverflow.com/a/3110563/3251909\">stackoverflow.com/a/3110563/3251909</a>"
