    "creation_date" : 1524667740,
    "answer_id" : 50025284,
    "question_id" : 2973041,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I like to use</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/util/Properties.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Properties</a></p>\n\n<p>Example:</p>\n\n<pre><code>Properties props = new Properties();\n\nprops.setProperty(\"displayName\", \"Jim Wilson\"); // (key, value)\n\nString name = props.getProperty(\"displayName\"); // =&gt; Jim Wilson\n\nString acctNum = props.getProperty(\"accountNumber\"); // =&gt; null\n\nString nextPosition = props.getProperty(\"position\", \"1\"); // =&gt; 1\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>If you are familiar with a hash table you will be pretty familiar with this already</p>\n"
