  "title" : "A KeyValuePair in Java",
  "body" : "<p>I'm looking for a KeyValuePair class in Java.<br>\nSince java.util heavily uses interfaces there is no concrete implementation provided, only the Map.Entry interface.</p>\n\n<p>Is there some canonical implementation I can import?\nIt is one of those \"plumbers programming\" classes I hate to implement 100x times.</p>\n"
